							<div class="bio-container">
					<div class="bio-img-container">
						<div class="bio-img">
							<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/amber-sparks-100x100.jpg" width="96" height="96" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/amber-sparks.jpg 2x" alt="Amber Sparks" class="avatar avatar-96 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-96 alignnone photo" />						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Amber Sparks</h4>
												<p>Amber Sparks is the author of <em>And I Do Not Forgive You, The Unfinished World and Other Stories<em>, and the short story collection, <em>May We Shed These Human Bodies,</em> as well as the co-author of a hybrid novella with Robert Kloss and illustrator Matt Kish, titled <em>The Desert Places</em>. She’s written numerous short stories, flash fictions and essays, which have been featured in various publications and across the web. Say hi on Twitter @ambernoelle.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			
